# README

The game is described here: 

https://cookieclicker.fandom.com/wiki/Garden

# Play

`npm install`

`npm run start`

How to play interactively:

- enter -> next tick
- p,0,1,2 -> plant `0` at `(1,2)`
- h,1,2 -> harvest plant at `(1,2)`
- a -> harvest all plants
